building VR that you interacted with the world with your hands.

39
00:02:02,110 --> 00:02:04,491
So we started work on this with a very early prototype of what

40
00:02:04,511 --> 00:02:05,911
would end up being the Vive.

41
00:02:06,591 --> 00:02:08,072
And one of the first things that we did

42
00:02:08,112 --> 00:02:10,512
was we built this demo where there was four boxes,

43
